Currently directory contains following files:
1) build_in_subdir.mk: Hook to create build directory in the source directory to house
        all the object files
2) common.mk: make fragment to collect sdk and platform related source and header include
paths based on the sdk configuration
3) rule.mk: make fragement to house all the common build commands to generate firmware
executable
4) stm32f4_buildenv.mk: stm32f4 chipset build make fragment to include toolchain
and chipset sdk header
5) openocd-configs: Directory contains configuration files to be used with openocd
        debugger tool
